eID Applet Service 1.2.0-SNAPSHOT API

The components within this package allow you to use the eID applet within a Java EE servlet container in a secure way.

See: Description

Packages 
Package Description
be.fedict.eid.applet.service
This package contains the service components.
be.fedict.eid.applet.service.dto
This package contains the Data Transfer Object tools.
be.fedict.eid.applet.service.impl
This package contains implementation specific classes.
be.fedict.eid.applet.service.impl.handler
This package contains implementation of message handlers.
be.fedict.eid.applet.service.impl.tlv
This package contains the TLV parser classes.
be.fedict.eid.applet.service.util
This package contains some utility classes.
The components within this package allow you to use the eID applet within a Java EE servlet container in a secure way. The most important servlet component is AppletServiceServlet.
